Net Income = Total prduction - upkeep - spending<br />
<br />
The spending part is having error<br />
<br />
Its supposed to be <br />
Spending = Reparing + ship pool + council tax<br />
<br />
It seems only the council tax is taken into account and not shipbuilding, thus resulting in much less spending than actual fact.<br />
<br />
I checked with another player and he has the same problem. Wonder if this problem is through out AS.						<P align=right> </P>
